extendedInfo.description: Fire up the message furnace with this gear-filled Steampunk theme for GOSMS Pro. Soot and oil are the delivery mechanism, for your messages when using this theme. Gears and cogs and ancient machines will liven up your phone with this grimy Steampunk  theme.Other Steampunk Themed GO Apps Also available in the market by mindseed design are:* Steampunk GO Launcher Ex* Steampunk GO SMS* Steampunk GO locker* Steampunk GO Contacts* Steampunk Calendar GO Widget* Steampunk Switch GO Widget* Steampunk Switch GO Widget 2* Steampunk Facebook GO Widget* Steampunk Twitter GO Widget* Steampunk Task Manager GO Widget* Steampunk Search GO WidgetSteampunk Widgets will be released one by one over the next few weeks.If you would like to contact me, please use any of the means below. I'm always happy to hear from you. Don't be shy.Follow: https://twitter.com/@mindseedDesignLike: http://www.facebook.com/mindseed.designPlus: https://plus.google.com/109275982008448960608/postsVisit: http://www.mindseed.co.zaEmail: mindseed.design@gmail.comPlease don't forget to rate - it makes all the time taken creating these for free worth it.keywords: steampunk theme, go sms pro, go sms, industry, android steampunk theme, mindseed design, mindseed, sms theme, go sms theme

reviews.title: Very excited!
reviews.comment: I have downloaded a lot of the steampunk themed apps etc... that you offer.  I can honestly say that all of the selections I have made have brought nothing but smiles to my face!   The only thing I REALLY wish I could get or figure out, is a way to predict the next word to text.  (I know, the issue MOST people want to do away with,right?!)  I need it though!!  Please help.

reviews.title: Awesome Theme and Branching Out
reviews.comment: Per my other review, this is awesome. I almost gave it 4 stars than realized my issue is not actually the designer of the app. But what irks me, and this is the same with all of these Themes, Widgets, Apps, is that in most causes they are overlaying stock resources and not replacing them (the services are still running in the back-ground, and unless you root the phone, killing them is not doing anything).  But the widget in conjunction with this app and the pop-up (blue) SMS thingy, are all a nice combo.
